high_descs: Move across the kitchen to the counter with tea kettle and tomato.
Pick up the fork that is on top of the papers beside the kettle
Move across the kitchen to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Open the cabinet immediately to the right of the fridge then place the fork into the cup in the cabinet.
Pick up the cup with fork in it in the cabinet, close the cabinet.
Move across the kitchen to the stove.
Place the cup with a fork in it beside the paper towel on the counter left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a fork in it on the counter beside the stove.

high_descs: Move to the island to the right before the stove
Pick up a fork from the island
Move to the cabinet to the right of the fridge
Place the fork in the cup in the cabinet
Pick up the cup from the cabinet
Move to the counter to the left of the stove
Place the cup on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork inside on the counter to the left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn around then move to the center of the kitchen island
Pick up the fork that is sitting on top of the counter
Carry the fork while moving to the cupboard that is to the right of the fridge
Open the cupboard under the counter and place the fork in the cup that is in the cupboard
Pick up the cup that has the fork in it from the cupboard
Carry the cup with the for in it and move to the right side of the stove
Place the cup with the fork to the left of the stove on the small counter top
anns.task_desc: Move a cup with a fork to the counter by the stove

high_descs: Turn around, then turn left, then turn right to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the fork on the kitchen island, next to the kettle.
Go around the kitchen island, then turn left to face the counter next to the fridge.
In the cabinet under the counter and next to the fridge, put the fork in the cup.
Pick up the cup in the cabinet.
Go around the kitchen island, then turn right to face the counter between the stove and the trash can.
Put the cup on the counter, next to the paper towel.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and take a step, then turn right again and walk up to the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal fork that is closest to the teapot on the kitchen island.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk around the kitchen island to the counter just to the right of the fridge.
Open the leftmost cabinet door in front of you and place the metal fork handle down into the glass that is inside the cabinet.
Pick up the glass with the metal fork inside of it and close the cabinet door.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and walk around the kitchen island to the small bit of counter top to the left of the stove.
Place the glass with the fork inside of it onto front right edge of the small bit of counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a metal fork inside of it on the counter.
